Now we need a partner
to help us

00:04:06,947 --> 00:04:09,015
scale up manufacturing
to meet the demand.

00:04:09,015 --> 00:04:13,120
So...Who wants to jump
in the water with us?

00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:15,088
HERJAVEC: Wow.
CORCORAN: Wow.
Remarkable.

00:04:15,088 --> 00:04:17,057
JOHN: Good, good, good.
